{"tid":300380,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"機場某電器鋪做左五年，你問我答","createTime":"2017-06-28T00:18:47.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-28T16:56:53.000Z","uid":108422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"50399be88095bff7286314aa7f2202055f40f2ed","tid":300380,"uid":108422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T00:18:47.000Z","msg":"識答一定答，勿相認<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c6da7509d8c2287f5c1840eaef65f6a41187b88","tid":300380,"uid":119596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T00:23:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"459c8fd0e51fa8ef470823c163558497f6db3063","tid":300380,"uid":108422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T00:29:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e38a04b91671513cd6b9f1f78fdadcb1321c2b6c","tid":300380,"uid":93231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T00:41:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>識答一定答，勿相認<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n想問下賣電器收入平均幾多，同埋好唔好做 ？"},{"pid":"ab1a7e7ac4999d1d516ca3e7aadbad01d4c991e7","tid":300380,"uid":108422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T00:49:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>識答一定答，勿相認<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n想問下賣電器收入平均幾多，同埋好唔好做 ？</blockquote><br />\n早幾年有蝗蟲就好做，你睇新聞日本人都比佢地養大胃口就知點解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好唔好做，多勞多得，早幾年你識基本野點賣下既，20-30k無問題，有時爆數出30K+<br />\n<br />\n而家少左人豪洗，平均16k-20K<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，真係超級好彩上面Target出鬆手就20K+"},{"pid":"23d2039d5d2c273667be297ddab90d82214d56ed","tid":300380,"uid":75674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T00:55:27.000Z","msg":"啲旅行用萬用頭無地線唔係唔賣得嫁咩？"},{"pid":"29ae9699a91ba974337b47965c68a3764cf5c8b9","tid":300380,"uid":108422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T00:58:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>啲旅行用萬用頭無地線唔係唔賣得嫁咩？</blockquote><br />\n呢個唔係咁清楚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我地由開業賣到而家都未出現話唔賣得既問題"},{"pid":"d1e91b7c38ed996d030c5085e199e6a6d93ebf58","tid":300380,"uid":108422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T16:56:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 開錯台潛得好快 無人想問就不推了"}]}